1
00:00:00,367 --> 00:00:01,367
I only got into this industry

2
00:00:01,368 --> 00:00:03,737
to follow the person I liked.

3
00:00:04,037 --> 00:00:05,357
I've never actually been in love.

4
00:00:05,972 --> 00:00:06,940
Him?

5
00:00:06,941 --> 00:00:08,040
I don't know.

6
00:00:08,041 --> 00:00:10,321
- I never told him how I felt.
- Are you really that busy?

7
00:00:11,044 --> 00:00:12,712
- My type?
- Have a seat.

8
00:00:13,046 --> 00:00:14,046
Not too short.

9
00:00:14,214 --> 00:00:15,214
Short hair.

10
00:00:15,382 --> 00:00:16,382
Naturally curly.

11
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:17,751
A great smile.

12
00:00:17,752 --> 00:00:18,918
Someone optimistic...

13
00:00:19,886 --> 00:00:21,654
who can balance out my negativity.

14
00:00:23,757 --> 00:00:26,092
We haven't talked since the wrap party.

15
00:00:26,793 --> 00:00:28,261
Are you actually that busy,

16
00:00:28,828 --> 00:00:30,163
or are you just dodging me?

17
00:00:32,132 --> 00:00:33,533
Work's been piling up lately,

18
00:00:34,667 --> 00:00:36,269
and I was worried you were still mad.

19
00:00:38,038 --> 00:00:40,073
I figured it'd be better to talk in person.

20
00:00:42,442 --> 00:00:43,810
I thought you'd explain

21
00:00:44,811 --> 00:00:45,811
that all of this

22
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:48,914
wasn't just an act...

23
00:00:48,915 --> 00:00:50,483
that you just couldn't help yourself.

24
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:53,953
I guess I was overthinking it.

25
00:00:54,754 --> 00:00:55,788
Anyway,

26
00:00:55,789 --> 00:00:57,891
I have a clear schedule today,

27
00:01:09,135 --> 00:01:10,703
so we can talk face-to-face.

28
00:01:11,137 --> 00:01:12,772
Just in case

29
00:01:13,173 --> 00:01:15,174
you try to use "work"

30
00:01:15,175 --> 00:01:16,342
to avoid me again.

31
00:01:19,813 --> 00:01:20,580
I'm going to touch up my makeup.

32
00:01:20,581 --> 00:01:21,614
See you on stage.

33
00:01:30,757 --> 00:01:31,925
Remember back then?

34
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:33,759
In that basic group chat,

35
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,195
I was your "study buddy."

36
00:01:36,062 --> 00:01:37,430
When I asked to meet,

37
00:01:38,832 --> 00:01:40,112
you claimed you were in a wreck.

38
00:01:41,301 --> 00:01:42,569
When I asked for a photo,

39
00:01:42,869 --> 00:01:44,437
you joked it wasn't "online dating."

40
00:01:45,572 --> 00:01:47,640
You ghosted me online,

41
00:01:48,083 --> 00:01:49,484
and now in real life,

42
00:01:49,509 --> 00:01:50,789
you're playing the amnesia card?

43
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:55,014
Let's see you try to hide now.
